'''Chrome線上應用程式商店'''（{{lang-en|Chrome Web Store}}）是[[Google|Google]]公司旗下的[[网络应用程序|网络应用程序]][[在线商店|在线商店]]，其于2010年5月19日的[[Google_I/O|Google I/O]]会议上公布，并于2010年12月6日正式开放。<ref>{{cite web |accessdate=2010-06-02 |url=http://www.businessinsider.com/google-launching-chrome-web-store-2010-5 |title=Google Launching "Chrome Web Store" |publisher=Business Insider |date=2010-05-19 |author=Saint, Nick |archive-date=2010-05-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100522105002/http://www.businessinsider.com/google-launching-chrome-web-store-2010-5 |dead-url=no }}</ref>该商店允许用户安装并运行专为[[Google_Chrome|Google Chrome]]浏览器制作的网络应用。<ref>{{cite web |accessdate=2010-06-02 |url=http://blog.chromium.org/2010/05/chrome-web-store.html |title=The Chrome Web Store |publisher=Google |date=2010-05-19 |author=Kay, Erik |archive-date=2013-08-17 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6IvpVykut?url=http://blog.chromium.org/2010/05/chrome-web-store.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

商店中的应用使用[[HTML|HTML]]或Chrome浏览器的扩展语言写成。<ref>{{cite web |accessdate=2010-06-02 |url=http://www.theregister.co.uk/2010/05/26/chrome_web_store_and_native_apps/ |title=Google hints at native code in Chrome Web Store |publisher=The Register |date=2010-05-26 |author=Metz, Cade |archive-date=2010-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100530025429/http://www.theregister.co.uk/2010/05/26/chrome_web_store_and_native_apps/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>其中的应用既有免费，亦有付费的。<ref>{{cite web |accessdate=2010-06-02 |url=http://techcrunch.com/2010/05/19/chrome-web-store/ |title=Google Previews Chrome Web Store — An App Store For The Web (If You’re Using Chrome) |publisher=TechCrunch |date=2010-05-19 |author=Siegler, MG |archive-date=2010-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100603022303/http://techcrunch.com/2010/05/19/chrome-web-store/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

宣告在2022年6月之前，終結所有的Chrome Apps。<ref>{{cite web |author1=雷鋒網 |title=Google 宣布兩年內關閉 Chrome Apps，拓展程式成壓倒駱駝的最後一根稻草 |url=https://technews.tw/2020/01/17/google-is-finally-killing-off-chrome-apps/ |website=TechNews 科技新報 |accessdate=2020-01-17 |archive-date=2020-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200117190754/https://technews.tw/2020/01/17/google-is-finally-killing-off-chrome-apps/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

